cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper deals with reinforcement learning in a multi-agent system, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with multi-agent systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of imitation learning, which is a subfield of robotics, suggesting that it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper deals with decentralized execution, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
